  <brief_title>The Effect of Hot Cataplasm With Caraway Oil in the Treatment of Irritable Bowel Syndrome</brief_title>
  <acronym>CarO</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomised Controlled Study on the Effect of a Kneipp Hot Cataplasm With Caraway Oil in the Treatment of Irritable Bowel Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
