  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a daily use of a Kneipp hot cataplasm with
      caraway oil is effective in the treatment of abdominal pain and complaints caused by
      Irritable bowel syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      see above.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
